          </dt>
          <dd class="mt-2 ml-16 text-base text-gray-500">
            Tasks can be assigned to external users through links, enhancing flexibility in task delegation.
          </dd>
        </div>

        <div class="relative">
          <dt>
            <div class="absolute flex items-center justify-center h-12 w-12">
