              </svg>
            </div>
            <p class="ml-16 text-lg leading-6 font-medium text-gray-900">To-Do List</p>
          </dt>
          <dd class="mt-2 ml-16 text-base text-gray-500">
            A built-in to-do list feature to help users keep track of tasks and deadlines effectively.
          </dd>
        </div>
      </dl>
